{"tid":1789543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對黃色經濟圈嘅少少睇法","createTime":"2019-12-19T11:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T12:35:41.000Z","uid":72497,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"285ec30afc81d6a5ee4d830afc992e9aed76677a","tid":1789543,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈嘅門檻唔需要高， 黐連儂牆 (定期更新)， 唔播tvb同店內播黃歌，就可以稱為黃店。就好似點可以減低犯罪，唔好嚴刑峻法咪得囉。同理想廣大黃色經濟圈，低門檻係最為有效嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n門檻逾低吸引藍店轉黃嘅機率就逾高。要知道我地唔止要令黃店逾開逾多， 仲要消滅藍店(壓縮佢哋嘅生存空間)，只要假以時日我地就可以見到成街都係黃店。 至於藍店？佢地已經唔存在啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76727f03c745fceabd559ed6bc94fdb8b5b85a1","tid":1789543,"uid":9151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"低門檻先易壯大 未壯大就要求多多就會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619a1190f3ea162b49178958aadb11b8740503d4","tid":1789543,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e76727f03c745fceabd559ed6bc94fdb8b5b85a1","tid":1789543,"uid":9151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"低門檻先易壯大 未壯大就要求多多就會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"冇錯，我見好多人都話要高門檻，我係唔明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5669963a28fbc0e1aff6e89ed6ff9717c99a835e","tid":1789543,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"壯大完再升級set死線麥麥77啦<br />\n如果個圈有得賺啲舖頭緊係唔想割"},{"pid":"f3bfdda9ae647656d6f4a05569b417b4fd18bf2d","tid":1789543,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"唔記得講低門檻嘅最大好處，就係當我地要三擺個時， 嗰啲偽黃店就一定要跟，咁個力量就可以好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa658fab13c1edd0dee4eaa1244e0e163dcaf75","tid":1789543,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim